  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>

        <div xml:id="Kali87-kilavi">
          <p type="edition">itu parattaiyarcēri ceṉṟamai aṟintilaḷeṉat talaivimāṭṭuc ceṉṟavaṉōṭu ivaḷ ūṭi 
            uṟaḻntu kūṟit tōḻi vāyilāka ūṭa-ṟīrvāḷ taṉ neñcoṭu kūṟiyatu.</p>
          <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"></p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="Kali87">
            <lg type="edition">
                <l>orūunī yeṅkūntal koḷḷalyām niṉṉai</l>
                <l>verūutuṅ kāṇuṅ kaṭai;</l>
                <l>teriyiḻāy! ceytava ṟilvaḻi yāṅkuc ciṉavuvāy</l>
                <l>meypirin taṉṉavar māṭṭu;</l>
                <l>ēṭā, niṉakkut tavaṟuṇṭō nīvīṭu peṟṟā</l>
                <l>yimaippi ṉitaḻmaṟai pāṅkē keṭuti</l>
                <l>nilaippā laṟiyiṉu niṉṉontu niṉṉaip</l>
                <l>pulappā ruṭaiyar tavaṟu;</l>
                <l>aṇaittōḷāy, tīyāraip pōlat tiṟaṉiṉ ṟuṭaṟṟuti</l>
                <l>kāyun tavaṟilēṉ yāṉ;</l>
                <l>māṉōkki nīyaḻa nīttava ṉāṉātu</l>
                <l>nāṇila ṉāyi ṉalitan tavaṉvayi</l>
                <l>ṉūṭuta leṉṉō viṉi;</l>
                <l>iṉi, yātumīk kūṟṟum yāmila maṉṟa</l>
                <l>takaiyatu kāṇṭaippāy neñcē paṉiyāṉāp</l>
                <l>pāṭilkaṇ pāyal koḷa.</l>
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                <l></l>
            </lg>
        </div>
